1. *Kučko* mi je spasilo život. (My puppy saved my life.)
2. *Kučka* sada ima svoje kućice. (The puppy now has its own house.)
3. *Kučke* su bile veoma druželjubive. (The puppies were very friendly.)
4. Ja sam jednom pronašao *kučka*. (I once found a puppy.)
5. Moj otac je uveo *kučka* u naš dom. (My father brought a puppy into our home.)
6. Moja *kučka* je postala velika. (My puppy grew up.)
7. Moje *kučko* je postalo jako veselo. (My puppy became very cheerful.)